eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.interfaces

Interface IExecutioner

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidController

    public interface IExecutioner
    Interface defining methods for the many ways to execute a command in JDroidLib! The name is a pun. A punny pun.
